Dotfile Readme
--------------

This is a readme file for my dotfiles.
Yadm is currently the tool I use to manage them.

yadm clone https://github.com/kyoto-shift/dotfiles


Requirements
------------
    - yadm
    - git, wget


Installs
--------
    - zsh/ohmyzsh
    - tmux
    - neovim + vim-plug


System Changes
--------------
    Headless:
        - provides tty colors (setvtrgb)
        - rebinds escape to caps lock (loadkeys)
